Class Docker

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.ApplicationListener

    public class Docker
extends com.badlogic.gdx.Game
    Author:
    HAL9000 Represents the application Docker. Manages the different screens and, in extension to the libGDX Game-class, it keeps a history for the screens, so you can easily return through the menu history.
